FREIGHTFLOW CRM
===============

HOW TO OPEN
Double-click "Start FreightFlow CRM.cmd".

The CRM opens in your default Windows web browser. No installation,
account, or internet connection is required for the app itself.

YOUR DATA
Customer records are saved in your web browser on this computer.
Use "Export backup" in the lower-left menu regularly. This creates a
CSV file that can be opened in Excel and imported back into FreightFlow.

MOVING TO ANOTHER COMPUTER
1. Export a backup on the old computer.
2. Copy this FreightFlow CRM folder and the exported CSV to the new PC.
3. Open FreightFlow and choose "Import backup".

NOTES
- The included sample customers can be edited or deleted.
- Marking a follow-up Done schedules the next reminder 14 days later.
- Keep the folder together; the HTML, CSS, and JavaScript files are all
  required.
